{"tid":1081590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向中俄展實力 美軍24架F-22阿拉斯加州排陣","createTime":"2019-03-28T11:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T13:03:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9c5a661ee0a19b5af15637759e9d6dd5871aaf29","tid":1081590,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190328/photo/bkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_01p.jpg?20190328080427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20190328080427&h=13f804c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-22（前）、E-3（後右）及C-17（後左）展開「大象漫步」。（美國空軍圖片）<br />\n1/4<br />\n太平洋地緣政治局勢持續緊張，美國空軍在阿拉斯加州舉行大型演習，24架F-22隱形戰機周二（26日）在基地的跑道上列隊排陣，對外展示前沿部署及可投射壓倒性的空戰能力。<br />\n<br />\n演習「極地力量」（Polar Force）為期兩周，在阿拉斯加州埃爾門多夫空軍基地舉行，其中一個環節是「大象漫步」（Elephant Walk），即以最小的間距首尾相連滑行，以便於最短時間內讓最多戰機起飛。參與的除了F-22，還有一架E-3空中預警機及一架C-17運輸機。<br />\n<br />\n在美國國防部的「大國競爭」戰略背景下，美軍近期不時高調以軍機，向中國及俄羅斯展示戰備力量。近年俄羅斯軍機不斷飛近阿拉斯加州，埃爾門多夫空軍基地接報後，兩架全副武裝的F-22立即升空攔截，期間獲得空中預警機支援。資料顯示，該基地至少部署47架F-22。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190328/photo/bkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_02b.jpg?20190328080427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_02b.jpg%3F20190328080427&h=a702f849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-22起飛參與演習。（美國空軍圖片）F-22起飛參與演習。（美國空軍圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190328/photo/bkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_03b.jpg?20190328080427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_03b.jpg%3F20190328080427&h=26279d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-22駐守阿拉斯加州，隨時攔截飛近的俄羅斯軍機。（美國空軍圖片）F-22駐守阿拉斯加州，隨時攔截飛近的俄羅斯軍機。（美國空軍圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190328/photo/bkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_04b.jpg?20190328080427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001_04b.jpg%3F20190328080427&h=173faa19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-22（前）及E-3（後）參與演習。（美國空軍圖片）F-22（前）及E-3（後）參與演習。（美國空軍圖片）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190328/bkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190328%2Fbkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001.html&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=64a14956\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190328/bkn-20190328080041153-0328_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"267a63c43bce06d0495e3b9baea523ddd4bfac47","tid":1081590,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"可唔可以一野ko 南海艦隊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f042f6ebda75d36f10840d0c952d46632e099c20","tid":1081590,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"咁大個外掛油箱"},{"pid":"aef436d53605924ed43fe1688ed3ba486bb0e573","tid":1081590,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f042f6ebda75d36f10840d0c952d46632e099c20","tid":1081590,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"咁大個外掛油箱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"喺未真正開戰前所有起飛F22都會開雷達信號放大器，所以掛乜都冇所謂"},{"pid":"3a519330b6026d47b3ab3a6bb6f00db426b032ba","tid":1081590,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:32:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fd434912fc8e8ac679b7603230d582a90e3bda3","tid":1081590,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"一部打到幾多部su35?"},{"pid":"35b4534275d9c81b737793216b11018a59480d62","tid":10815